Package cz.vse.java.utils.lists.stringLists

Class StringBlackList

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.vse.java.utils.lists.stringLists.StringBlackList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IRestrictionsList, IStringRestrictionsList
    public class StringBlackList
extends java.lang.Object
implements IStringRestrictionsList

    Class of StringBlackList is used for containing list of all acceptable values.

    The class implement's IRestrictionsList for higher variability to use it anywhere it's needed.

    The main reason to use it is to collect all the needed values and be able to work with them interactively and intuitively as much as possible.

    THREAD-SAFE using CopyOnWriteArrayList Written for project "Utils".
    Version:
    26. 02. 2020
    Author:
    Vojtěch Pavlů
    See Also:
    IRestrictionsList, IStringRestrictionsList, StringWhiteList, List, CopyOnWriteArrayList
